trans-unit.note: Table Seminar Registration Header - NamedType RecordNameCannotBeModified
trans-unit.target: Nazwa rekordu nie może zostać zmieniona.

trans-unit.source: Only Planned seminars can be deleted
trans-unit.note: Table Seminar Registration Header - NamedType SeminarCannotBeDeletedIfPlanned

trans-unit.source: Cannot change Bill-to Customer No. if record is registered.
